metadata.name: MEMORY 016
metadata.description:
The Memory Collection is based on a series of found disks from my early childhood. Each piece contains a different collage of physical elements, typography, hand-style graffiti & rendered illustrations that celebrate a lifespan.

This collection was inspired by our inclination to reminisce, the universal experience of life & death, and the idea that Memories are the final by-product of our shared existence in life.
